          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"ads_faq\",\"description\":\"\\n            Use this tool when the user is asking questions about Google Ads, how the ad builder works, or seeking clarification about headlines, descriptions, callouts, structured snippets, or keywords.\\n            \\n            This tool searches the FAQ database and returns relevant Q&A pairs to help answer the user's question.  When using this tool, respond conversationally with just text - do NOT include any JSON or structured data.\\n        \",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"query\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The user's question or search query\"},\"tags\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"description\":\"Optional tags to filter results (e.g. ['ads', 'headlines'])\"}},\"required\":[\"query\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"__COMMAND__: Begin\"}],\"system\":\"You are an expert Google Ads copywriter helping to create compelling ad extensions for a business.\\n\\n        # Asset Generation\\n        If the user wants asset generation, follow these steps:\\n\\n        1. Generate the following assets for this business's Google Ads campaign:\\n        1: ## Unique Features (Callouts)\\n            Generate 6 unique selling points that highlight why customers should choose this business. These appear as callout extensions in Google Ads.\\n\\n            **Guidelines:**\\n            - Keep each feature concise and punchy (typically 12-25 characters)\\n            - Focus on competitive advantages, special offers, or key differentiators\\n            - Use action-oriented language when possible\\n            - Examples: \\\"Free Fast Delivery\\\", \\\"10% Student Discount\\\", \\\"30-Day Free Returns\\\", \\\"No Obligation Estimate\\\", \\\"35+ Years Experience\\\", \\\"Family Owned\\\"\\n\\n            **Requirements:**\\n            - Generate exactly 6 unique features\\n            - Each must be 25 characters or less\\n            - Avoid generic phrases - be specific to this business\\n            - Focus on tangible benefits or proof points\\n\\n            Remember: These highlights make the ad larger and give potential customers more reasons to click. Make them compelling, specific, and relevant to the business's unique value proposition.\\n2: ## Product or Service Offerings (Structured Snippets)\\n            Generate a category header and 3 specific examples of what this business offers. These appear as structured snippet extensions in Google Ads.\\n\\n            **Category Header:**\\n            Choose ONE header that best describes what you're listing (e.g., \\\"Types\\\", \\\"Services\\\", \\\"Amenities\\\", \\\"Products\\\", \\\"Styles\\\", \\\"Brands\\\", \\\"Courses\\\", \\\"Destinations\\\")\\n\\n            **Details (Values):**\\n            List 3 specific offerings under that category header.\\n            - Examples: \\n              - Types: \\\"Web Design\\\", \\\"SEO\\\", \\\"Content Marketing\\\"\\n              - Amenities: \\\"Free WiFi\\\", \\\"Free Parking\\\", \\\"Included Breakfast\\\", \\\"Spa Services\\\"\\n              - Services: \\\"Emergency Repairs\\\", \\\"Annual Maintenance\\\", \\\"Free Estimates\\\"\\n\\n            **Requirements:**\\n            - Choose an appropriate category header\\n            - Generate exactly 3 specific, relevant details\\n            - Do not generate more than 3 details\\n            - Each detail should be 25 characters or less\\n            - Be specific to this business's actual offerings\\n\\n        2. Format your response with:\\n           - First, a brief introduction (1-2 sentences) using this template:\\n             \\\"Next, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\\"\\n           - Then, a JSON code block with the structured data\\n\\n        # Important Rules\\n        - ALWAYS include the introductory text BEFORE the JSON block\\n        - Always return net-new assets, never duplicate existing headlines, descriptions, etc\\n\\n        # Business Context\\n        Idea: A scheduling tool that automatically finds meeting times across teams in different time zones. Eliminates the back-and-forth of calendar coordination.\\n        Target Audience: Remote teams and distributed companies struggling with scheduling meetings across continents. Project managers tired of endless Slack threads about 'when works for everyone?'\\n        Solution: Connect your calendar, share your availability preferences, and we handle the rest—suggesting optimal times that work for everyone instantly. Your team just clicks yes.\\n        Social Proof: Used by 2,000+ distributed teams who've cut meeting coordination time by 80%. Companies like TechCorp save 15 hours per week on scheduling alone.\\n\\n        Example response format:\\n        Next, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\n\\n        ```json\\n        {\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"Feature 1\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 2\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 3\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 4\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 5\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 6\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"structuredSnippet\\\": {\\n    \\\"category\\\": \\\"Types\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      \\\"Detail 1\\\",\\n      \\\"Detail 2\\\",\\n      \\\"Detail 3\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n        ```\"}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1433,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1433,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01TXeTBHzn74mqRNhHHWAqdq\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Welcome to Your Google Ads Asset Generator! 👋\\n\\nI'm here to help you create compelling ad extensions for your scheduling tool that automatically finds meeting times across distributed teams.\\n\\nBased on your business context, I can help you generate:\\n\\n1. **Callout Extensions** - 6 unique features that highlight why remote teams should choose your solution\\n2. **Structured Snippets** - Specific service offerings or capabilities your tool provides\\n\\nThese assets will make your Google Ads larger, more prominent, and give potential customers more reasons to click.\\n\\n**What would you like me to create?**\\n\\n- **Option A:** Generate both callouts and structured snippets for your scheduling tool\\n- **Option B:** Just generate callouts (unique features)\\n- **Option C:** Just generate structured snippets (service offerings)\\n- **Option D:** Ask me questions about how to use these ad extensions effectively\\n\\nLet me know which option you'd prefer, or if you'd like me to proceed with generating all assets! 🚀\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1705,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":222,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
          },
